Detection

The email appears suspicious due to:

- Unofficial sender domain (office365-support-mail.com)
- Urgent message about mailbox issue
- Contains external link for upgrade
----
Analysis

1. Sender Analysis:
- Domain is not official Microsoft domain
- Likely spoofed email

2. URL Analysis:
- Link "office365-secure-upgrade.net" is not legitimate
- Could lead to phishing website

3. Social Engineering:
- Creates panic ("Mailbox full")
- Forces immediate action
----
Containment

- Email marked as spam/phishing
- Suspicious domain flagged
- Users advised not to interact
- Link blocked (simulated)
